{"tid":1948593,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"英國官員對「中共」不滿","createTime":"2020-03-29T06:16:12.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-07T07:47:42.000Z","uid":134071,"like":54,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":31,"replies":[{"pid":"4f08c438afc0695cb2aae1ec91c1d630a1bf3707","tid":1948593,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-29T06:16:12.000Z","msg":"英國官員不滿「中共」隱瞞疫情<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://na.cx/i/49ocheu.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F49ocheu.jpg&h=4a94b06e&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.dailymail.co.uk/news/article-8163767/Downing-Street-says-China-faces-reckoning-coronavirus.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dailymail.co.uk%2Fnews%2Farticle-8163767%2FDowning-Street-says-China-faces-reckoning-coronavirus.html&d=XV0%2F%2BsWk6HIEEz5%2BsPHJeyVDAD9kR8TUwRzNJuuVR5U%3D&h=fa63d008\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.dailymail.co.uk/news/article-8163767/Downing-Street-says-China-faces-reckoning-coronavirus.html</a><br />\n<br />\nBoris Johnson&rsquo;s allies turned on China over the coronavirus crisis yesterday, as Britain&rsquo;s death toll from the epidemic reached four figures.<br />\n<br />\nMinisters and senior Downing Street officials said the Communist state now faces a &lsquo;reckoning&rsquo; over its handling of the outbreak and risks becoming a &lsquo;pariah state&rsquo;.<br />\n<br />\nThey are furious over China&rsquo;s campaign of misinformation, attempts to exploit the pandemic for economic gain and atrocious animal rights record.<br />\n<br />\nThe Prime Minister, who now faces Cabinet calls to reverse his decision to let controversial Chinese firm Huawei build large parts of Britain&rsquo;s new 5G telecoms network, today warns that the epidemic is likely to worsen in the coming weeks &ndash; but that he expects the British &lsquo;spirit&rsquo; to overcome the crisis."},{"pid":"aba55e22024c48cbcbc9b81c35b3c040f2576ec2","tid